144
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,957
There you go, lad. All right.

145
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:45,919
Here we go.

146
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,274
-Whoa, whoa.
-Where's my boy?

147
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,759
