150
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,429
- Aye, strong.
- He'll show 'em.

151
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,839
Ain't that right, Jenny?

152
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:58,230
He'll be home bouncing Charlie and Ailish
on his knee again in no time.

153
